    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my reliable ride. It's been such a great car for me and is still in wonderful shape, ready for its next adventure! Everything runs smoothly, and it's been really well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one for you. I'd love to see it go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
