    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-limited slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a recent refresh of the suspension bushings to preserve original turn-in characteristics. Maintenance is current, including a dual-VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement for long-term mechanical reliability. While the exterior shows light honest wear, the drivetrain and hydraulic steering rack offer the precise feedback expected of a well-sorted M-car.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
