    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 Toyota 4Runner TRD Off-Road that strikes the perfect balance between trail-ready grit and suburban comfort. The exterior is finished in a classic metallic silver that holds a brilliant luster; while the body is straight and free of major dents, there are a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips on the hood typical of responsible use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of utility and cleanliness. The dark grey bolstered seats show minimal bolster wear and are entirely free of tears or odors. Every button, dial, and digital interface\u2014from the touchscreen infotainment to the Crawl Control system\u2014operates exactly as the factory intended. Mechanically, this vehicle is exceptionally sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a thick folder of receipts to prove it. The engine idles quietly and pulls strong, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the 4WD system engages effortlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh fluid flush and a new set of all-terrain tires with deep tread depth. If you are looking for a dependable, honest vehicle that has many miles of adventure left in it, this 4Runner is ready for your inspection.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
